    "Similar to the derivation in the TAT-QA dataset this script is crucial to steer our model to use a tool instead of producing the answer directly.",
    "Similar to TAT-QA, this dataset consists of questions over tabular data and unstructured text across diverse domains (Chen et al., 2021).",
    "The majority of questions necessitate multi-hop inference involving both forms of data.",
    "The dataset's relevance lies in its omission of derivation or intermediate steps, which poses a challenge for the model to infer the correct answer.",
